        "TileImage": "$($repository 7d28ed81-2b13-4a8f-8276-0216c5e8058d).Image",
        "Description": "Stuyvesant and Ingram are the main targets here. But... We can&apos;t risk to leave her daughter and his surname out there. The journalist knows what is happening and he wasted every penny he won on that Pulitzer thing on a hit on The Vulture. We&apos;re here already, so why not. Al-Ghazali has been a very good Providence asset and i&apos;m sure that he would be very dangerous in a post-Providence world, so we can retire him early.",
